title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Port of Miami
description:
In this video we will have a look at the free addon which has been released for the Port of Miami for MSFS 2020. The addon contains both the cargo and cruise terminals and is located close to Fisher Island and connect to the city of Miami itself.

If you would like to try the scenery yourself, download it via the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/31526/port-of-miami-and-cruise-ship-terminal-miami-fl-usa
